explanation: [0-0] Against a white background, a woman wearing a printed hoodie and black pants looks forward, holding a corn cob between her hands with her left hand underneath and her right hand on top.

[0-6] The woman in black raises her right hand and lowers her left hand, making the corncob float in front of her. Then, she places her hands on both sides of the corncob and turns her body, clenching her fists and moving them to the sides of her body as she dances. It is revealed that the woman has a fork in her mouth, which is inserted into the corncob.
